WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 24]

01:16.830 --> 01:19.010
Master is at Hushe Peak.

01:20.830 --> 01:22.140
Jiaping's distant-sensing talisman?

01:24.080 --> 01:25.090
He's in danger.

01:25.640 --> 01:26.290
Jiaping?

01:27.750 --> 01:28.580
Have you found him?

01:32.640 --> 01:33.530
Where is Hushe?

01:34.110 --> 01:34.810
What happened?

01:36.240 --> 01:38.620
It's Hushe Peak, the secret forbidden area of Wuyue Court.

01:41.910 --> 01:42.780
I'll go back with you.

02:01.390 --> 02:01.980
My Lord.

02:05.030 --> 02:05.780
Rakshasa.

02:11.030 --> 02:12.970
You finally remember me, My Lord.

02:17.320 --> 02:19.090
You slew Zong Quan

02:19.590 --> 02:21.250
and rid the demon clan of Longming Sanctuary.

02:21.900 --> 02:23.780
Truly a joyous victory!

02:26.990 --> 02:28.340
Through the chaos in the Yue State,

02:29.800 --> 02:32.570
you've seen clearly

02:32.590 --> 02:34.650
the shameless faces of all immortal sects.

02:39.040 --> 02:41.940
What's the difference between the immortal sects or the demon clan?

02:43.110 --> 02:45.690
All schemes for petty self-interest.

02:46.670 --> 02:49.650
I ordered you to return. Why didn't you?

02:51.480 --> 02:54.570
Five centuries ago, we crossed the East Sea.

02:54.900 --> 02:56.410
You said back then

02:56.870 --> 02:59.060
this would be our new home.

03:00.240 --> 03:01.060
Have you forgotten?

03:04.320 --> 03:05.780
Now I'm reborn as a mortal.

03:06.550 --> 03:09.250
All the past means nothing to me.

03:10.150 --> 03:11.370
I came to you for another matter.

03:12.240 --> 03:15.180
Lifei and I are going to Hushe Peak.

03:16.620 --> 03:17.740
Jiang Lifei again.

03:18.320 --> 03:19.970
She is merely an ordinary woman.

03:20.270 --> 03:21.620
You are the great Demon Lord.

03:21.760 --> 03:23.370
Would you abandon your grand cause

03:23.390 --> 03:24.250
and sink low for her?

03:24.480 --> 03:26.250
You keep addressing me as My Lord,

03:26.320 --> 03:27.650
yet you act on your own

03:28.430 --> 03:30.060
and question every choice I make.

03:32.620 --> 03:36.220
Do you expect me to obey you instead?

03:46.430 --> 03:48.300
I... I dare not.

04:05.830 --> 04:07.340
You came back, after all.

04:12.360 --> 04:15.810
Master, I wish to borrow the Hexagonal Prism.

04:17.080 --> 04:20.180
I fear once you uncover the truth you seek,

04:20.790 --> 04:24.570
you'll sink into mire with no escape.

04:26.760 --> 04:27.450
My senior brother

04:29.560 --> 04:31.810
and the old man who raised me

04:34.120 --> 04:35.420
must be waiting for me.

04:58.350 --> 05:03.570
Lifei, we shall be master and disciple for all time.

05:06.390 --> 05:10.100
Zhuiyu Peak will always be your home.

05:19.580 --> 05:20.100
Go.

05:22.600 --> 05:27.000
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

05:27.290 --> 05:29.440
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

05:29.610 --> 05:35.240
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

05:35.320 --> 05:39.360
♪Let frost, snow and rain block the long stone steps♪

05:39.480 --> 05:41.680
♪I tread fleeting mist beneath my feet♪

05:41.800 --> 05:47.480
♪At last I see, life's end lies boundless wild free♪

05:47.800 --> 05:58.880
♪Don't idle away time. We shall meet atop the peak♪

06:05.980 --> 06:07.620
Yangling, that's the direction of Wengu Hall.

06:07.980 --> 06:09.420
It's demonic energy! Go.

06:33.270 --> 06:34.370
Why is the maple forest stretching further?

06:36.520 --> 06:38.810
You're too hasty and fell for an illusion.

07:17.880 --> 07:18.860
Are we at home?

07:25.320 --> 07:27.980
No, we're still on Hushe Peak.

07:45.440 --> 07:46.060
Watch out!

08:03.230 --> 08:04.130
Where are we?

08:06.390 --> 08:08.810
I've heard that when immortal cultivators reach a certain realm,

08:09.390 --> 08:10.180
they can open

08:10.200 --> 08:11.450
a private world of their own,

08:12.200 --> 08:14.370
complete with mountains, rivers, sun, moon, and boundless clouds.

08:15.590 --> 08:16.770
They set all the laws

08:17.150 --> 08:18.570
governing this realm,

08:19.230 --> 08:22.010
which is known as a miniature realm.

08:23.560 --> 08:24.010
Whose

08:24.680 --> 08:26.210
miniature realm is this?

08:33.830 --> 08:34.890
It's Cuihua Peak's restriction spell.

08:36.750 --> 08:39.660
This must be Cuixuan's miniature realm.

08:41.960 --> 08:43.180
Where's the Hexagonal Prism?

08:54.080 --> 08:54.570
Go.

09:06.800 --> 09:08.690
Didn't expect Cuixuan's miniature realm

09:09.400 --> 09:11.060
to have such thick spirit energy.

09:12.160 --> 09:13.850
Is this Hushe Peak's secret?

09:19.040 --> 09:19.690
What's up?

09:22.230 --> 09:23.610
I sensed weird energy all around.

09:24.990 --> 09:28.180
Feels like demonic energy, but not quite.

09:29.320 --> 09:31.850
Why would demonic energy exist in an immortal secret land?

10:00.510 --> 10:01.900
Flowers growing out of skeletons.

10:02.350 --> 10:05.380
They live off demonic energy

10:05.400 --> 10:06.090
and vengeful spirits.

10:06.960 --> 10:09.490
The more hatred, the brighter the flowers.

10:14.350 --> 10:15.210
Their roots trap

10:15.920 --> 10:17.690
lost, unwilling souls

10:17.870 --> 10:19.540
in dirty mud,

10:21.440 --> 10:24.090
with no escape forever.

10:25.990 --> 10:26.940
All these demon bones

10:27.440 --> 10:29.300
had their power sucked dry when they lived.

10:31.040 --> 10:32.810
Is this Zong Quan's Spirit-Devouring Art?

10:33.320 --> 10:37.140
No, it's Wuyue Court's Spirit-Binding Art,

10:37.750 --> 10:39.850
same as the binding barrier of Lilie Valley.

10:41.800 --> 10:45.540
You mean Cuixuan's trained by using demon spirits?

10:59.350 --> 11:00.330
Human hearts carry dark schemes.

11:01.320 --> 11:06.060
What's the difference between the immortal sects or the demon clan?

11:11.800 --> 11:14.610
Calm down. Don't turn into a Yecha.

11:17.350 --> 11:18.140
I'm fine.

11:20.230 --> 11:21.260
No aura here.

11:22.470 --> 11:25.660
No traces of living things are left here. Let's leave.

11:26.350 --> 11:26.900
Wait.

11:29.960 --> 11:31.780
There's a faint aura lingering.

12:10.160 --> 12:10.970
Who are you?

12:26.110 --> 12:27.690
The spirit energy doesn't work at all, Xiuyuan.

12:35.870 --> 12:36.730
His heart meridians are severed.

12:38.110 --> 12:38.940
He won't make it.

12:40.440 --> 12:41.140
No.

12:41.510 --> 12:43.140
As long as he is alive, there will be hope.

12:58.660 --> 12:59.260
Lifei.

13:04.800 --> 13:05.730
Sir, hold on.

13:06.110 --> 13:07.140
I'll get you out of here.

13:11.080 --> 13:11.660
Don't move.

13:17.280 --> 13:18.090
How could this happen?

14:24.560 --> 14:25.330
Qingcheng.

14:26.560 --> 14:27.180
Go.

14:33.200 --> 14:34.260
Master.

14:41.630 --> 14:42.490
Master!

14:45.800 --> 14:46.730
Master!

14:46.750 --> 14:47.090
Lifei.

14:47.110 --> 14:48.020
Master!

14:48.400 --> 14:48.970
Lifei.

14:49.710 --> 14:50.570
Go.

14:51.320 --> 14:52.730
- Let's get out of here. - No!

14:52.750 --> 14:55.570
No! Master!

14:55.990 --> 14:58.330
Don't leave me!

15:01.280 --> 15:03.690
Don't abandon me!

15:05.470 --> 15:08.450
Master! Master!

15:11.510 --> 15:13.570
Master! Master!

15:17.230 --> 15:18.380
- Master! - Lifei.

15:18.560 --> 15:19.180
Master!

15:40.110 --> 15:41.260
Master!

15:42.320 --> 15:43.420
Master!

15:56.560 --> 15:57.610
Qingcheng!

16:20.320 --> 16:24.210
Foolish brats, how dare you ruin my secret realm!

16:24.800 --> 16:26.490
So this is indeed your miniature realm.

16:28.830 --> 16:32.210
It's you! You killed him.

16:34.040 --> 16:35.780
You killed my master!

16:36.560 --> 16:37.540
Your master?

16:38.080 --> 16:39.210
I'll kill you!

16:45.680 --> 16:46.210
Lifei!

16:56.560 --> 16:57.490
Demons.

16:58.400 --> 17:00.570
They're demon spies. Seize them!

17:01.750 --> 17:04.660
Jiang Lifei, Lei Xiuyuan, you have nowhere to run.

17:16.160 --> 17:17.290
Dead as you are,

17:17.710 --> 17:19.690
your remnants still dare stir trouble.

17:20.230 --> 17:22.450
Do you think destroying my miniature realm

17:22.470 --> 17:24.580
and crippling my spirit roots can stop me?

17:24.600 --> 17:25.660
Listen!

17:25.680 --> 17:27.420
That girl is your disciple.

17:27.920 --> 17:31.050
The Senluo Grand Art must be on her.

17:31.070 --> 17:34.290
Qingcheng, be patient.

17:34.790 --> 17:36.580
I'll bring her back soon.

17:36.840 --> 17:37.900
Once I fetch her,

17:38.160 --> 17:40.900
you can reunite with her.

18:47.400 --> 18:49.620
Zhaomin, what are you doing here?

18:49.990 --> 18:50.730
Qin.

18:54.990 --> 18:56.900
I should be asking you the same.

18:57.510 --> 18:58.940
This is near Zhuiyu Peak.

18:59.340 --> 19:00.860
Where did you come from?

19:01.070 --> 19:02.820
You nearly scared Zhaomin.

19:05.310 --> 19:06.970
I was ordered to capture demon spies.

19:09.340 --> 19:10.420
Demon spies?

19:11.710 --> 19:12.450
Where?

19:18.100 --> 19:18.860
Where are they?

19:20.310 --> 19:20.940
She and I?

19:21.960 --> 19:22.530
No.

19:23.230 --> 19:24.380
We only planned

19:24.400 --> 19:26.100
to pick fresh morning herbs together.

19:26.270 --> 19:28.380
Why call us spies, Yangling?

19:28.640 --> 19:29.820
What's your deal?

19:30.200 --> 19:31.820
Who said you're demon spies?

19:32.230 --> 19:35.010
You just said it, right?

19:35.100 --> 19:35.860
You heard clearly, huh?

19:37.440 --> 19:37.970
Yangling,

19:38.230 --> 19:40.580
do you think everyone's a spy?

19:41.160 --> 19:44.490
You even accused Lifei before.

19:46.710 --> 19:47.290
I know the truth.

19:47.880 --> 19:49.940
She rejected you,

19:49.960 --> 19:51.140
so you're jealous of her.

19:51.160 --> 19:51.690
You!

20:05.070 --> 20:06.730
Can't believe you struck out!

20:07.160 --> 20:08.210
Zhaomin, back me up.

20:08.710 --> 20:10.180
He threw the first punch.

20:10.880 --> 20:13.140
I won't back down from a fight.

20:13.160 --> 20:15.340
Come on, let's settle this.

20:20.640 --> 20:22.180
Don't run. Let's go to Cuixuan...

20:22.960 --> 20:24.580
Stop pretending. Go check how they are.

20:40.600 --> 20:42.420
Are you okay? Bad injuries?

20:43.200 --> 20:45.580
We're fine. Why are you here?

20:45.990 --> 20:47.970
Master noticed the Hexagonal Prism went haywire

20:48.230 --> 20:49.290
and sent us to help you.

20:56.680 --> 20:57.820
Tell him I'm thankful.

20:59.160 --> 21:01.490
What happened last night could get him into trouble.

21:02.310 --> 21:04.420
It's fine. He knows how to handle it.

21:04.960 --> 21:07.140
But look, it's daytime now.

21:07.400 --> 21:09.210
The whole sect is under strict guard.

21:09.680 --> 21:10.940
How will you escape?

21:13.360 --> 21:15.660
Don't worry. I know a hidden path in the mountains.

21:15.880 --> 21:17.290
You can leave without being noticed.

21:17.710 --> 21:19.210
No more delays, let's go.

21:21.230 --> 21:21.770
Watch your step.

21:22.400 --> 21:23.340
- Stay safe, Lifei. - This way.

21:25.120 --> 21:25.530
Hurry up.

21:28.160 --> 21:28.820
That's impossible.

21:29.960 --> 21:32.290
Xiuyuan is quiet and stubborn,

21:32.960 --> 21:34.340
but he always respects his masters and behaves properly.

21:34.790 --> 21:36.900
He's never done anything to betray the sect.

21:38.200 --> 21:41.100
Cuixuan, you said they're demon spies.

21:41.160 --> 21:41.940
Got any proof?

21:42.550 --> 21:45.250
Lei Xiuyuan and Jiang Lifei snuck into the forbidden area at night,

21:45.270 --> 21:46.250
releasing demonic energy.

21:47.640 --> 21:50.860
If they aren't spies, how can they use demonic arts?

21:52.200 --> 21:55.290
As to what happened at Lilie Valley last time,

21:56.880 --> 21:58.380
they must be guilty.

21:59.230 --> 21:59.820
Cuixuan,

22:00.510 --> 22:02.050
you personally chose

22:02.070 --> 22:03.580
those top disciples

22:03.680 --> 22:04.970
to fix the valley barrier back then.

22:07.470 --> 22:08.050
Yes.

22:09.200 --> 22:11.140
They had injuries all over them,

22:11.790 --> 22:13.690
but you forced them to go.

22:13.960 --> 22:15.970
I tried talking you out of it, but failed.

22:17.270 --> 22:19.210
As for the demonic energy on them,

22:19.440 --> 22:21.860
they probably got tainted

22:21.960 --> 22:23.730
when fighting demons.

22:24.880 --> 22:28.050
Cuixuan, what's hidden

22:28.790 --> 22:30.530
in Hushe Peak's forbidden area?

22:30.750 --> 22:32.250
Don't you know

22:32.400 --> 22:34.010
why I lock Hushe Peak up?

22:34.840 --> 22:37.900
I know well if someone's

22:38.600 --> 22:40.450
tainted or using demonic arts.

22:40.840 --> 22:41.940
I wouldn't frame them.

22:43.270 --> 22:44.210
Easy there, Cuixuan.

22:44.790 --> 22:45.490
Chongyi

22:45.510 --> 22:47.450
only wants what's best for Wuyue Court.

22:48.070 --> 22:50.940
This must be a misunderstanding, I think.

22:51.270 --> 22:52.140
Misunderstanding?

22:52.840 --> 22:54.580
Jiang Lifei is always stirring up trouble.

22:55.310 --> 22:57.900
I bet she dragged Xiuyuan into all this.

22:58.510 --> 22:59.450
Nonsense!

22:59.840 --> 23:02.010
Lei Xiuyuan lured her instead!

23:02.100 --> 23:03.690
I'm still mad thinking about it.

23:03.840 --> 23:04.820
Last time in Duantu,

23:04.920 --> 23:06.940
Jiang Lifei was weak,

23:06.960 --> 23:08.210
and Lei Xiuyuan actually...

23:09.600 --> 23:10.900
I don't even want to say it out loud.

23:15.960 --> 23:18.100
Cuixuan, your aura is unstable.

23:18.400 --> 23:19.770
Looks like your spirit energy backfired on you.

23:20.230 --> 23:21.340
Did you get hurt?

23:23.640 --> 23:25.820
Those two spies ambushed me.

23:26.160 --> 23:28.820
I let my guard slip, but I'm fine.

23:29.470 --> 23:30.860
Brief meditation is enough.

23:31.100 --> 23:31.970
It's simply out of line!

23:33.680 --> 23:35.210
I mean Lifei and Xiuyuan.

23:36.600 --> 23:38.770
Cuixuan, take care.

23:39.230 --> 23:40.770
I'll fetch them back right now.

23:41.640 --> 23:42.210
Don't worry.

23:48.100 --> 23:50.820
Chongyi, I'll come with you.

24:28.310 --> 24:29.970
Xiaobangchui, what are you doing at the door?

24:29.990 --> 24:32.050
Put medicine on my injuries and wrap them.

24:59.680 --> 25:00.420
Master,

25:00.990 --> 25:02.820
you must've waited for me so long.

25:04.160 --> 25:05.730
I finally found you.

25:07.160 --> 25:07.860
I finally

25:09.200 --> 25:10.250
found you.

25:55.310 --> 25:57.860
Go ahead and cry if you want to.

26:04.990 --> 26:06.770
Master didn't like seeing me cry.

26:11.100 --> 26:12.250
I'll hold it in.

26:13.710 --> 26:15.340
I won't make him fret over me.

26:28.510 --> 26:29.450
I'll grab some food.

27:05.750 --> 27:09.730
As the Demon Lord, you'd let a woman order you around.

27:20.750 --> 27:21.380
My Lord,

27:23.960 --> 27:27.290
Jiang Lifei is the Divine Tree, right?

27:39.680 --> 27:41.490
Blame me for being blind

27:41.990 --> 27:43.580
to her true identity.

27:44.920 --> 27:45.690
Then again,

27:46.550 --> 27:48.290
every Demon Lord ends up falling for the Divine Tree.

27:49.100 --> 27:51.530
This is our chance to restore the demon clan.

27:52.510 --> 27:54.900
When are you going to absorb her spirit power?

28:05.600 --> 28:06.580
Leave her alone.

28:08.400 --> 28:10.660
Did you forget you're Yecha?

28:14.100 --> 28:15.140
For hundreds of years,

28:16.070 --> 28:17.210
no Demon Lord

28:17.230 --> 28:19.180
has broken this curse.

28:20.340 --> 28:21.940
No matter how dedicated

28:21.960 --> 28:22.900
or loving you are,

28:23.550 --> 28:25.210
the Fruit of the Divine Tree

28:26.030 --> 28:28.010
will lure you without fail.

28:28.790 --> 28:30.250
It's just your nature as Yecha.

28:31.400 --> 28:33.420
If you can't bear to do it yourself,

28:35.750 --> 28:37.290
I'll handle it for you.

28:44.680 --> 28:45.250
My Lord,

28:46.680 --> 28:48.250
are you really going to kill me?

28:58.880 --> 29:03.380
After the heaven's wrath, spirit energy grew scarce on the islands,

29:04.030 --> 29:05.660
and our clansmen could barely survive.

29:06.750 --> 29:07.820
You promised

29:08.640 --> 29:12.380
you'd take us back to the Central Plains,

29:12.600 --> 29:13.620
so we could survive.

29:15.470 --> 29:17.940
Five centuries ago, after you disappeared,

29:18.640 --> 29:20.940
the immortal sects hunted our clansmen down.

29:21.270 --> 29:22.900
We were almost wiped out.

29:24.070 --> 29:26.420
My Lord, only by absorbing the Divine Tree's power

29:27.600 --> 29:29.210
can you gain your Yecha power

29:30.030 --> 29:32.050
and find our clansmen a way out.

29:33.550 --> 29:37.380
I live only for you and our clansmen,

29:38.070 --> 29:39.290
at all costs, without regret.

29:39.790 --> 29:42.250
But snap out of it, My Lord.

29:42.680 --> 29:44.970
Save our dying clansmen.

30:02.160 --> 30:02.690
My Lord.

30:05.510 --> 30:06.620
You're badly hurt.

30:06.960 --> 30:08.860
If you don't absorb the Divine Tree's power, your soul will split apart,

30:08.880 --> 30:09.770
and you'll die in terrible pain.

30:09.790 --> 30:10.970
I know my own fate!

30:14.920 --> 30:16.180
If you touch her even once,

30:17.750 --> 30:19.250
no matter what you've done for me,

30:19.960 --> 30:21.010
I'll kill you.

30:21.120 --> 30:22.860
I've always been ready to die

30:22.880 --> 30:24.770
for you at all times. But what about her?

30:25.400 --> 30:27.340
Are you going to abandon all of us

30:27.360 --> 30:28.450
and risk your life for her?

30:29.360 --> 30:30.380
I'm Lei Xiuyuan.

30:32.160 --> 30:35.690
Nothing will ever change that.

30:43.640 --> 30:44.140
My Lord.

30:47.840 --> 30:50.900
My Lord, don't blame me.

30:53.640 --> 30:55.580
All is for our clan's future.

31:15.750 --> 31:18.140
Lifei, eat something.

31:20.070 --> 31:20.770
I'm okay.

31:22.920 --> 31:23.690
I wished to burn

31:23.710 --> 31:25.730
fine robes for Master,

31:27.200 --> 31:28.180
yet all are ragged.

31:33.600 --> 31:35.050
His final robes were tattered

31:37.200 --> 31:38.580
beyond recognition.

31:57.270 --> 31:57.860
Lifei,

32:01.160 --> 32:01.940
that strap.

32:10.880 --> 32:12.290
Master left it for me.

32:13.920 --> 32:15.250
There must be a story behind it.

32:37.550 --> 32:38.900
Why's there nothing on it?

32:41.070 --> 32:44.180
Master, what did you want me to know?

32:47.270 --> 32:48.290
Xiuyuan, check this with me.

32:54.680 --> 32:55.290
Xiuyuan!

32:55.640 --> 32:57.860
Come out! We saw you.

32:58.960 --> 33:00.180
You have no place to run.

33:01.160 --> 33:03.530
Guangwei and I are here for you two.

33:04.070 --> 33:05.210
Only he and I,

33:06.600 --> 33:08.210
but you can't get away.

33:09.880 --> 33:12.690
Wait, this place reeks of heavy toxic mist.

33:13.070 --> 33:14.660
Nobody could stay here.

33:16.840 --> 33:18.210
That way, go.

33:25.510 --> 33:27.450
This place is even worse.

33:27.600 --> 33:28.900
Let's go back there.

33:29.270 --> 33:31.450
Which path? We've wandered all night.

33:31.710 --> 33:33.290
You've been looping around, huh?

33:34.030 --> 33:35.820
Guangwei, don't lose your temper.

33:36.030 --> 33:37.690
Calm down. Here is the case.

33:37.710 --> 33:40.290
Look, Qingqiu is huge,

33:40.310 --> 33:41.940
plus this heavy toxic fog.

33:41.960 --> 33:43.420
It messes up our spirit energy,

33:43.640 --> 33:46.050
so it's normal to get lost.

33:46.070 --> 33:47.340
Are you here to track them,

33:47.680 --> 33:48.970
or sneak them a warning?

33:48.990 --> 33:49.970
What are you saying?

33:49.990 --> 33:51.730
I'm obviously here to track them.

33:51.880 --> 33:53.290
Never mind, I'll look by myself.

33:55.510 --> 33:57.860
Alright, you lead.

33:59.070 --> 34:01.340
Watch out. Don't fall into the ditch.

34:09.160 --> 34:10.620
Xiuyuan, hang in there.

34:13.880 --> 34:15.300
The Ganhua Realm saved you last time.

34:16.070 --> 34:17.170
It'll help you again.

34:34.440 --> 34:35.970
No matter how dedicated

34:35.990 --> 34:37.050
or loving you are,

34:37.630 --> 34:39.220
you'll absorb the Divine Tree's power.

34:43.190 --> 34:45.420
What's wrong? Feeling sick?

34:48.670 --> 34:49.260
Xiuyuan.

34:49.440 --> 34:50.900
I'm okay. Don't come close.

34:58.720 --> 35:01.220
Is your injury hurting? Let me check.

35:01.510 --> 35:02.380
Stay away from me.

35:11.110 --> 35:14.300
Lei Xiuyuan, are you crazy?

35:15.460 --> 35:16.740
You never mentioned your bad injuries.

35:17.070 --> 35:18.380
Now you're pushing me away.

35:22.420 --> 35:23.700
If something bad happens to you...

35:28.340 --> 35:29.170
Listen up,

35:30.780 --> 35:33.570
I'd rather die than let you die.

35:38.420 --> 35:39.490
All of you

35:40.940 --> 35:41.860
must live.

35:42.820 --> 35:43.650
No one's dying!

35:47.550 --> 35:48.260
Lifei.

35:49.820 --> 35:53.510
♪The warmth within my arms♪

35:53.890 --> 35:56.930
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

35:57.230 --> 36:00.630
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

36:00.990 --> 36:04.260
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

36:04.630 --> 36:07.830
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

36:08.150 --> 36:11.350
♪I can no longer tell you♪

36:11.750 --> 36:14.920
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

36:14.920 --> 36:15.900
Don't push me away.

36:15.900 --> 36:18.270
♪Utter that line♪

36:18.650 --> 36:19.720
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

36:19.720 --> 36:20.820
I know nothing.

36:20.820 --> 36:22.840
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

36:22.860 --> 36:24.130
