36:25.550 --> 36:26.780
or when something goes wrong.

36:26.780 --> 36:27.610
♪You're still screaming♪

36:27.890 --> 36:29.800
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

36:29.800 --> 36:31.420
You'd keep it a secret even if you died.

36:32.860 --> 36:33.260
I just...

36:33.260 --> 36:36.890
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

36:37.030 --> 36:38.650
I'm right there,

36:39.860 --> 36:41.260
yet I know nothing.

36:41.260 --> 36:46.990
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

36:46.990 --> 36:48.610
What do you want me to do?

36:48.610 --> 36:49.800
♪Just to keep you safe♪

36:49.820 --> 36:51.050
What should I do?

36:55.480 --> 36:59.090
♪My breath is about to stop♪

36:59.210 --> 37:02.730
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

37:02.850 --> 37:06.290
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

37:06.450 --> 37:09.240
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

37:09.640 --> 37:13.020
♪I smile as it ends♪

37:13.440 --> 37:16.840
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

37:17.200 --> 37:20.400
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

37:20.720 --> 37:23.880
♪To light your way through the night♪

37:24.000 --> 37:25.720
