37:53.270 --> 37:54.950
♪Who says that love and hate♪

37:56.990 --> 37:57.610
Xiuyuan.

37:57.610 --> 38:00.080
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

38:00.320 --> 38:02.160
♪I will level the seas and mountains♪

38:02.980 --> 38:03.860
