38:45.980 --> 38:48.970
Yue, who are you really?

39:00.190 --> 39:03.570
I'm Rakshasa, the demon clan's Guardian.

39:09.420 --> 39:13.170
In primordial times, ancient gods cursed the Yecha clan.

39:13.980 --> 39:16.420
If they don't absorb the Divine Tree's purest spirit power,

39:17.070 --> 39:20.380
